OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784636312
OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FThe United States has carried out its
OL,7,Fninth successive night of airstrikes
OL,8,Fon Iran, hours after announcing the
OL,9,Fdeath of another American service
OL,10,Fmember.
OL,12,FPresident Donald Trump said the
OL,13,Fstrikes were carried out in honour of
OL,14,FUS troops killed in recent attacks,
OL,15,Fsaying: "We hit them very hard again
OL,16,Ftonight."
OL,18,FIran retaliated by launching an attack
OL,19,Fon Bahrain, the home of the US Navy's
OL,20,F5th Fleet, and Kuwait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
