PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784636312
OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FThe latest hostilities showcase the US
OL,7,Fand Iran inching closer to all-out war
OL,8,Fonce again, after last month's interim
OL,9,Fdeal, meant to end fighting
OL,10,Fpermanently, has crumbled and shipping
OL,11,Ftraffic in the Strait of Hormuz has
OL,12,Fstalled.
OL,14,FBoth sides have largely targeted
OL,15,Fcivilian infrastructure relied on by
OL,16,Fmillions of people.
OL,18,FThe US military said the service
OL,19,Fmember was killed in Iraq on Saturday
OL,20,Fduring the "controlled detonation" of
OL,21,Fa downed Iranian drone.
OL,26,@|D@LOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
