PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784636312
OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FThe strikes by the US military's
OL,7,FCentral Command mark the ninth
OL,8,Fstraight night of hostilities. There
OL,9,Fwas no immediate word from Iran on any
OL,10,Fcasualties or damage from the attacks,
OL,11,Fbut Iranian state media reported
OL,12,Fexplosions being heard in southern and
OL,13,Fnorthwestern Iran.
OL,15,FTrump has threatened to target Iran's
OL,16,Fpower stations and bridges to try to
OL,17,Fcompel Tehran to loosen its hold on
OL,18,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, which saw one-
OL,19,Ffifth of global traded oil supplies
OL,20,Ftransit before the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
