PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784636312
OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FRecent attacks suggest the US military
OL,7,Fis carrying out that plan.
OL,9,FThe US in the past week reimposed a
OL,10,Fnaval blockade on Iranian ports to
OL,11,Fhalt its shipments of crude oil. The
OL,12,Fmilitary on Saturday said it had
OL,13,Fredirected six ships and disabled one
OL,14,Fsince then.
OL,16,FThe halfway point has passed in the 60
OL,17,Fdays that the deal set out to
OL,18,Fnegotiate the permanent end of the war
OL,19,Fand other issues, including Iran's
OL,20,Fnuclear programme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
