OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio told
OL,7,Freporters that the US is still open to
OL,8,Fnegotiating with Iran but that "it has
OL,9,Fto be real".
OL,11,F"We're going to continue to respond.
OL,12,FIf the door opens to diplomacy - if
OL,13,Fthe guys that want to do something
OL,14,Fproductive for Iran win and take
OL,15,Fcontrol of that system, or take
OL,16,Fcontrol of the negotiations - that'll
OL,17,Fbe a very positive development," Rubio
OL,18,Fsaid. "That's not where we are
OL,19,Ftonight, unfortunately."
