OL,3,CTrump expands strikes on Iran 'in
OL,4,Chonour of' soldiers killed
OL,6,FIranian authorities on Sunday said at
OL,7,Fleast 50 people have been killed and
OL,8,F517 wounded in the latest rounds of US
OL,9,Fstrikes.
OL,11,FSince the war began on February 28, 17
OL,12,FUS service members have been killed.
